ISLAMABAD, Apr 30 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Saturday thanked Allah Almighty for blessing her with the pilgrimage of Holy Kaaba and Masjid-e- Nabvi (S.A.W).
The minister, in a tweet, said the honour of Tawaf of Khana Kaaba, performing Umrah and the visit to the Masjid-e-Nabavi (S.A.W) were a spiritual experience, which could not be described in words.
